episodes.title: SCIENTOLOGY: The American Cult
episodes.description:
Join me as I dive deep into Scientology in Clearwater, Florida — its origins, beliefs, and why this city has become the movement’s global headquarters. I explore the history of Scientology, its unique practices and structure, and uncover what really happens inside the organization’s presence in downtown Clearwater.
But things take a strange turn… as I’m filming, members of the Sea Org begin following me and even start taking pictures.
🔹 History of Scientology in Clearwater
🔹 Key beliefs and daily practices
🔹 The power and mystery of the Sea Org
🔹 What it’s like walking through Scientology’s city
👉 Watch until the end — things get intense.
#Scientology #ClearwaterFlorida #SeaOrg #DarinT #FloridaHistory #HiddenFlorida
